{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8901d4b5ed","title":"“入党条件”","origin":"《重庆市右派言论选辑第一集》（内部文件，只供领导同志参考，请勿外传和翻印），中共重庆市委宣传部办公室编印，1957年8月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c65d0a54f0","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"8901d4b5ed"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"7fe8902b9e","name":"重庆师范专科学校"},{"id":"951771b4cb","name":"魏佐治"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"04e711bac9","type":"title","text":"“入党条件”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8901d4b5ed"},{"id":"f19e7e7fbf","type":"authors","text":"重庆师范专科学校魏佐治","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8901d4b5ed"},{"id":"b2e8a6430b","type":"paragraph","text":"[编者按：魏佐治，男，重庆师专学生，家庭出身地主，青年团员。本人曾参加过狂飙社，学联票友社。魏在这次鸣放运动中表现对党极为不满，抓住个别党员的缺点加以扩大、丑化，写出所谓“入党条件”污蔑党，和歪曲党员的形象。]","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8901d4b5ed"},{"id":"ed6f0e849e","type":"paragraph","text":"根据我们在原来工作的单位亲眼看到的，(现在还是如此)某些党组织在发展党员中修改了党章，把入党标准规定为下列这几项：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8901d4b5ed"},{"id":"acbf155be6","type":"paragraph","text":"1．除了工农出身以外，一概不要。(工农出身原来就有无产阶级思想省得教育)","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8901d4b5ed"},{"id":"17a373b423","type":"paragraph","text":"2．必须是女的。(男的爱说爱闹危险)","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8901d4b5ed"},{"id":"87c196a631","type":"paragraph","text":"3．必须是老好人。(不开腔，最稳当)","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8901d4b5ed"},{"id":"eb84b95dda","type":"paragraph","text":"4．必须是年轻人。(年老的社会关系复杂，了解起来困难)","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8901d4b5ed"},{"id":"b5d26455eb","type":"paragraph","text":"5．必须是能力不强的人。(能力强的不好对付)","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8901d4b5ed"},{"id":"69f8d06401","type":"paragraph","text":"6．必须是党员的爱人。(一家人，最放心)","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8901d4b5ed"},{"id":"243d16dfae","type":"paragraph","text":"7．必须是对领导毫无反对意见的人。(叫做党性强，才好管)","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8901d4b5ed"},{"id":"62d49c4fb9","type":"paragraph","text":"8．必须请党员吃油大。(这叫靠拢党)","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8901d4b5ed"},{"id":"7ddd785689","type":"paragraph","text":"9．必须是行动匆忙的人。(这叫做积极)","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8901d4b5ed"},{"id":"4ae433cf2b","type":"paragraph","text":"10．必须是“善于”体现领导意图的人。(其实是吹牛拍马)","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8901d4b5ed"},{"id":"8b50327f1c","type":"paragraph","text":"造成的结果是，新党员，戳一下，动一下，不起作用，在工作或学习上落后于群众，群众不满意，在党和非党群众之间筑起了一道墙。……最后失去了党的战斗力。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8901d4b5ed"},{"id":"1c75aceab5","type":"paragraph","text":"我们希望党取缔这样不合理的标准。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8901d4b5ed"}],"page":{"id":"c0d656a314","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8901d4b5ed","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}